info:
职位描述:
1.线上：根据需求，与文案策划配合完成微信海报长图、海报动图、H5、视频平面分镜等;
2.线下：包装设计、手册、易拉宝、折页、活动视觉设计等。

岗位要求:
1.在读本科或研究生，平面设计、视觉设计、新媒体传播相关专业;
2.熟练掌握AI、PS等设计软件、掌握简单视频剪辑能力，具备AICG、手绘能力者优先考虑;
3.有扎实的美术功底和图案设计能力，良好的创意思维和色彩搭配能力;
4.良好的沟通能力、团队协作能力;
5.热爱生活、爱看展、爱拍照、热爱学习新知识、新技能。

实习生需一周4天以上的到岗，大三、大四学生，4-6个月实习
人在上海，公司在上海市嘉定区南翔，通勤超过1小时不考虑

PURPOSE


	This position involves the pharma excipients registration, cosmetic new ingredient registration, usage of SAP database, and usage of chemistry knowledge to ensure that Lubrizol products can comply with varies regulations and customer requirements. And it offers the chance for the position holder to learn more about a career in product steward service for products, and the knowledge on SAP database, cosmetic regulations, pharma excipient regulations, and industry chemical regulations as well.





	RESPONSIBILITIES / ACCOUNTABILITIES


	•Assist in the preparation and submission of excipient application dossiers, and new cosmetic ingredient application dossiers;


	•Assist in regulatory monitor and provide regulatory communications/supports to customers and businesses;


	•Assist in regulatory reports/statements preparation;


	•Assist in SharePoint information maintain;


	•Support other PSCD function teams as needed;





	REQUIREMENTS


	Education Background


	•University students with a Master degree in chemical related major;


	Technical Skills & Experiences Preferred


	•Good oral/written English level;


	•Strong orientation toward daily customer service environment; detail oriented;


	•Strong knowledge of Microsoft Office Applications including Access, SharePoint a plus;


	•Excellent oral / written communication and interpersonal skills;


	•Self-motivated and comfortable working in a team environment;


	•Available at least 3 days per week;

The Role:

-Work with professional experienced insurance brokers to coordinate business cooperation.
-Technical supports, with insurance background or relevant experiences.
-Preparation of placing paper work.
-Support other member to organize some trainings and seminar to the client.

The Requirements:
-Bachelor degree or above and major in law, Finance, Accounting or Insurance;
-Fluent written and oral English;
-Basic Insurance knowledge and insurance experiences is preferred;
-Skills of presentation, negotiation and coordination;
-Team work, learning and hardworking willingness.
